\n \n Philadelphia Eagles\n Draft History\n \n

\n\t\t\n\t\n\t

Team Names: Philadelphia Eagles, Phi/Pit Eagles/Steelers

\n\t

Seasons: 93 (1933 to 2025)

\n\n\t

\n\t\tRecord (W-L-T): \n\t\t649-645-27\n\t

\n\n\t

Playoff Record: 29-27

\n\n\t

\n\t\tSuper Bowls Won:\n\t\t2 \n\t\t(5 Appearances)\n\t

\n\n\t

\n\t\tChampionships Won*:\n\t\t5\n\t

\n\n\t

\n\t\tAll-time Passing Leader: Donovan McNabb 2,801/4,746, 32,873 yds, 216 TD\n\t

\n\t

\n\t\tAll-time Rushing Leader: LeSean McCoy 1,461 att, 6,792 yds, 44 TD\n\t

\n\t

\n\t\tAll-time Receiving Leader: Harold Carmichael 589 rec, 8,978 yds, 79 TD\n\t

\n\t

\n\t\tAll-time Scoring Leader: David Akers 1,323 points\n\t

\n\t

\n\t\tAll-time AV Leader: Jason Kelce 132 AV\n\t

\n\t

\n\t\tWinningest Coach (including playoffs): Andy Reid 140-102-1\n\t
